Add @tahini{100%g}, @garlic{3%cloves}(crushed), and @lemon juice{1%dl} to a #food processor{}, and mix for about ~{2%minutes} until it starts looking like whipped cream. -- Add about 1 tbsp of ice water if mixture is too thick to emulsify.

Add @canned chickpeas{690%g}, @olive oil{0.5%dl}, @cumin{1%tsp}, @salt{1%tsp} and mix until smooth and creamy. Gradually add up to @ice water{3%dl} until you reach the consistency you want.

Garnish with @smoked paprika{1%tsp}.
